000Z","msg":"11/20"},{"pid":"88e9bf8e3fd5021a15f60b4ead51210bd96cc397","tid":1624353,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"12/20"},{"pid":"a63b73f138cf34874cea67554b02563ae34dacb4","tid":1624353,"uid":292698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:19:20.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大家要記住 <br />\n我地嘅制裁係要同對家嘅行為對等<br />\n<br />\n姐係例如，狗而家想殺人 我地殺狗就係天公地道 大家嘅武力咁就對等啦<br />\n<br />\n又例如，啲狗因爲見到人跳閘呢個罰500嘅小錯處，就沖上去毆打平民，咁係使用過分武力，係錯嘅<br />\n<br />\n咁呢我覺得美心呀 中銀呀 360果啲呢 我地只需要罷買罷食 做文宣 唱衰佢 禁佢飛仔 取消中銀嘅戶口etc 就夠啦 唔好做多 <br />\n裝修呢啲辛苦野 留番黎對付狗 對黑社會 對政權 又或者果啲直接幫助呢個極權嘅機構 例如黨鐵 啦<br />\n<br />\n要時刻記住 我地唔可以俾憤怒主導我地嘅行為<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地絕對唔可以 唔可以 成為我地最痛恨嘅人</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1841923c29a2923c3b3aa9341645ab7b7387d597","tid":1624353,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd1887e0438bd6bfe8a22feb897254b60360b96","tid":1624353,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:39:31.000Z","msg":"1/20"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人至今仍然輸緊 3000:0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b84a57ac807ba1def90ffe3236d6ebeefd091ed9","tid":1624353,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd1887e0438bd6bfe8a22feb897254b60360b96","tid":1624353,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:39:31.000Z","msg":"1/20"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人至今仍然輸緊 3000:0 <img src=\"/assets